Uniwersal instalance
-> pip install flask opencv-python socket

Install for Linux/ Ubantu/ RasberryPi:
-> sudo apt-get install python3-flask python3-opencv python3-socket

Install for anaconda/ miniconda users:
-> conda install flask opencv-python socket

You may have issues with downloading opencv libary, if you do try insted:
-> python3 -m pip install opencv-python
